author: Kuokka77
description:
"The BOOM BOOM ROOM" by AceMan, 3rd at BOOM! Party 2025 A500 music compo.
"Crash Course" by JazzCat, 1st at BOOM! Party 2025 A500 music compo.
1st art "Sentinel of Time" by Vasyl/Joker^Nah-Kolor^TRSI, 1st at BOOM! Party 2025 A500 gfx compo.
2nd art "Hungry Tension" by Koyot1222/Resistance, 6th at BOOM! Party 2025 A500 gfx compo.

00:00 The BOOM BOOM ROOM
02:19 Crash Course

A500 r5 audio. ProTracker 2.3F (8bitbubsy).

This rev 5 had a permanently enabled LED filter. LED turns on/off when you try to change the state in ProTracker settings, but no effect on audio.
It is hardware bypassed here with a couple of bridges in LF347N (chip U14) using 150 Ohm resistors.
title: Amiga music: AceMan & JazzCat - The BOOM BOOM ROOM & Crash Course (A500r5🎧Dolbyfied - filter bypass)
